N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 319.304 - Meat stews

State Regulations

Meat stews such as "Beef Stew" or "Lamb Stew" shall
contain not less than 25 percent of meat of the species named on the label, computed on the weight of the fresh meat. Notes
